      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Clara Swinson was appointed Director General for Global and Public Health in November 2016. 
Her previous roles include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Director of Adult Social Care Policy</li>
  <li>Director of Health Protection</li>
  <li>Deputy Director, Cross Government Obesity Team</li>
  <li>Principal Private Secretary to the Secretary of State for Health</li>
  <li>Health account manager, Prime Minister’s Delivery Unit</li>
</ul>

<p>She lives in London with her partner and 2 children.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_3823">
            <h1 id="director-general-global-and-public-health">Director General, Global and Public Health </h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Part of the Department of Health senior team and an executive member of its board, the Director General is responsible for leading the department’s public health teams, including:</p>

<ul>
  <li>emergency preparedness and health protection policy</li>
  <li>population health</li>
  <li>EU, international and prevention programmes</li>
  <li>health and work unit</li>
</ul>

<p>The Global and Public Health Group sponsor 4 arm’s length bodies:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Public Health England</li>
  <li>Human Fertilisation and Embryology Authority</li>
  <li>Human Tissue Authority</li>
  <li>NHS Blood and Transplant</li>
</ul>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care">Department of Health and Social Care</a>
</p>

            </div>
</section>      </div>




